The requirements for our software is as follows:

1. The system shall allow a user to create an account
2. The system shall save user account information
3. The system shall connect users sharing the same event
4. The system shall allow users to share an event
5. The system shall allow users to upload audio files
6. The system shall allow users to upload video files
7. The system shall allow users to upload image files
8. The system shall allow users to upload text files
9. The system shall allow users to remove their uploaded files
10. The system shall integrate into internet services
11. The system shall connect events with a geographical location
12. The system shall connect with a news article relating to the event
13. The system shall allow creation of a timeline for events
